ICommandLauncher - Interface in invoker
This interface defines the methods that all command launcher should implement..
incrementerDebut() - Method in class observer.ObservableBuffer
Increases the initial cursor by one position if the text has not ended.
incrementerDebut() - Method in interface receiver.MoteurEditeur
Increases the visible cursor one position
incrementerDebut() - Method in class receiver.MoteurImpl
 
incrementerFin() - Method in class observer.ObservableBuffer
Increases the selection cursor by one position if the text has not ended.
incrementerFin() - Method in interface receiver.MoteurEditeur
Increases the selection cursor one position (Selection is defined as characters between visible cursor and selection cursor)
incrementerFin() - Method in class receiver.MoteurImpl

Inserts the character given into the initial cursor position.
